ovde.

711
01:33:23,437 --> 01:33:25,731
Da li imamo uslove?

712
01:33:29,902 --> 01:33:31,862
Imamo uslove.

713
01:33:39,286 --> 01:33:42,831
Poslacu svoje lekare.

714
01:33:44,291 --> 01:33:48,462
-Salaam alaikum.
-Alaikum salaam.

715
01:34:07,940 --> 01:34:11,193
Ja sam Rejnald od Šatinjona!

716
01:34:51,525 --> 01:34:54,027
Na kolena.

717
01:34:56,113 --> 01:34:58,407
Niže.

718
01:35:00,909 --> 01:35:04,663
Ja sam Jerusalim.

719
01:35:06,748 --> 01:35:10,002
A ti, Rejnalde...

720
01:35:09,877 --> 01:35:13,213
ceš mi dati poljubac mira.

721
01:35:31,899 --> 01:35:33,984
Straža.

722
01:35:41,575 --> 01:35:44,912
U šta gledaš?
Mrtvog coveka.

723
01:35:44,912 --> 01:35:47,956
Rejnald de Šatinjon,
uhapšen si...

724
01:35:48,040 --> 01:35:50,125
i osuden.

725
01:35:52,961 --> 01:35:55,756
Dodi.

726
01:36:06,809 --> 01:36:10,145
Ako nastaviš ovako...

727
01:36:10,062 --> 01:36:12,564
moracu da ti nadem svrhu.

728
01:36:12,564 --> 01:36:14,650
Ako te Bog poštedi, to jest.

729
01:36:14,650 --> 01:36:16,819
Bog me ne poznaje.

730
01:36:16,944 --> 01:36:18,612
Da, ali te ja poznajem.

731
01:36:42,052 --> 01:36:44,763
Trebam te u Jerusalimu.

732
01:37:28,015 --> 01:37:31,018
- Salaam alaikum.
- Alaikum salaam.

733
01:37:38,025 --> 01:37:41,361
Zašto si se povukao?

734
01:37:41,361 --> 01:37:44,490
Zašto?

735
01:37:44,490 --> 01:37:48,660
Bog mu nije bio naklonjen. Samo Bog
može odluciti ishod bitke.

736
01:37:48,535 --> 01:37:51,997
Ishod bitke je odreden
od strane boga...

737
01:37:51,997 --> 01:37:55,417
ali i pripremama, brojem...

738
01:37:55,334 --> 01:37:59,296
odsustvom bolesti
i kolicinom dostupne vode.

739
01:37:59,296 --> 01:38:03,675
Ne može se održati opsada
sa neprijateljem na ledima.

740
01:38:03,550 --> 01:38:08,263
